==Korean==
===Noun===
'''두루미''' (''durumi'')  
# [[crane]], cf. Hungarian [[daru]] (perhaps of Sumerian origin), Japanese [[鶴]] (つる, tsuru)  

====Synonyms====
* [[선학]] ([[仙鶴]], ''seonhag, -hak'') literally, "hagio-crane"
* [[학]] ([[鶴]], ''hag, hak''), cf. the prefix of [[hagiography]] 
 
====See also====
* [[해오라기]] (''haeoragi'') white [[heron]], [[egret]]
* [[황새]] (''hwangsae'') [[stork]]

